+# Security notes
+
+- Do NOT commit secrets (JWT secret, keystores, certificates) to the repository.
+- Use GitHub Secrets / Azure Key Vault / other secret store for production secrets:
+  - COOLAPP_API_JWT_SECRET
+  - ANDROID_KEYSTORE_BASE64, ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD, ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS, ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD
+- For local development, use appsettings.Development.json and local keystores (not checked in).
+
+Additional recommendations:
+- Use HTTPS for backend in production and enforce ValidateIssuer/Audience in JWT options.
+- Consider refresh tokens and token revocation in production systems.
+- Store long-lived secrets in a dedicated secret store (KeyVault, AWS Secrets Manager, etc.).
